    "en": {
      "title": "Protesters detain Energy Secretary",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Employees of the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) staged a protest at the Power and Energy Ministry premises at Mal Road, Colombo 7 this afternoon (27) against the proposal to hand over petrol stations to foreign companies.",
        "The protesters surrounded the vehicles of the Secretary to the Ministry of Energy MPDUK Mapa Pathirana and later detained him at the Ministry premises.",
        "Afterwards, Secretary to the Ministry Mapa Pathirana gave a discussion to the protesters."
      ],
